Former President of Tunisia Zine El Abidine Ben Ali is sentenced to 20 years imprisonment in absentia by a Tunisian military court for inciting murder and violence during the revolution that ousted him from power in January 2011. (Reuters) (Al Jazeera)A woman is killed and 12 other people injured in a series of hit and run incidents in Cardiff, south Wales. A 31-year-old van driver is arrested by police. (BBC) (Western Mail) (The Guardian)